(234913, 7881, 234877, 'Birdshooter007', 3199, '', 1325315682, '[QUOTE=SHIEKH TARIQ UK;234877]SALAM BROTHERS.\nI have three HW 100S,HW98 and HW80 they are all in.22 and I really like the build and ruggedness.\nSH TARIQ UK.[/QUOTE]\nWeihrauchs or the HW80 is aka "the workhorse", they are very rugged and powerful, and very accurate. But I feel they are too heavy once you have a scope and mount on them, like a 4-16X50AO, you have to have support.', 1, 1, '119.73.0.228', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
