one to be there just in case.\n\nOn point 2: Agreed again. The sights should really be removable. \n\nIn 100k there is just the box, gun, two mags and a manual. Accessories are optional. Dunno how much they cost. As far as parts, I raised that question with the distributor and he assured me parts will not be a problem and the guns will come with warranties. (Something which we really need around here)[/quote]', 1, 0, '117.102.45.212', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
