(241193, 1888, 54876, 'Slayerjatt', 203, '', 1327232772, 'having bought 2 packs of gamo match pro pellets yesterday and with no place to shoot firearms i decided to try out my gamo cadet after over a year. i bought this gun in 2009 from al-syaad, dubai for about rs. 9000/- but didn''t shoot it much and it has been lying around without any cleaning or proper storage. \r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0037.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nmy brother yardie jutt and i had already broke a few wall tiles in such endeavours so we were warned to have a pellet trap to ensure there would be no collateral damage. here is what we did:\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0029.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0028.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\ntwo plastic bags filled with sand to catch the pellets were put inside the shoe box. although most of the pellets were caught inside the bags still the gun seemed to out power the set up resulting in this:\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0061.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0060.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nso we put two plastic bottles filled with water under the sand bags to stop the already slowed pellets and  after that there were no over enthusiastic pellets. :p\r\n\r\nthe range (approximately 10 meters)\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0030.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0034.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nthe shooters:\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0044.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0050.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nfirst target shot to adjust the sights:\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0082.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nsecond target: two strings of 5 shots each shooter.\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0083.jpg[/IMG]\r\n\r\nwe both were able to shoot 44/50 with somewhat controlled shooting with breath control while casual shooting scores averaged 38. the gun is quite powerful and capable of shooting bulls in the hands of the right shooter.\r\n\r\n[IMG]http://i570.photobucket.com/albums/ss141/slayerjatt/DSC_0087.jpg[/IMG]', 1, 1, '119.152.14.27', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
