(241840, 7857, 241832, 'AK47', 162, '', 1327418782, '[QUOTE=Ameer;241832][B]Nice successive shots sir. Personally i like free sights (no dots) for target shooting but for SD i am into dotted sights (2-dot or 3-dot).[/B]\n\n[COLOR=#ff0000][B]Now last question Sir[/B][/COLOR], since i am making up my mind to get another handgun in april (compact versions only), its a tie between[B] Caracal-C and CZ-Compacts[/B]. [B]Which dealer in Lhr/Pesh has these Caracals nowadays, or a premier importer of it?[/B]\n\n\n\nregards[/QUOTE]\n\n\nThank you Ameer bro, always nice to have interaction with you, coz you care to go into the technical perimeters of things. This is vital to understand one''s aspirations, there''s more to it than just the final check at shops for fit in hand. My personnel purchases too always have a very long prelude for selection.\n\nAs for CZ compacts vs Caracal, well, quite coincidentally, I had just completed comparison photographs/technical details, and was waiting for a couple of details before posting it.\n\nIt''s a tough choice, reason why I personally chose to be [I]double-covered[/I], with one of each. For the aspirant with only 1 compact/CCW in mind, a couple of things laid before to ease the selection would probably be a good thing to have here, yet let''s see, if I venture further onto it.\n\nFinally, as concerns your[I] last question[/I]:\n\n[I][B][COLOR=#40e0d0]I truly wish you could have spared me[/COLOR][/B][/I]\n\n[I][B][COLOR=#008000]I truly wish you could have spared me[/COLOR][/B][/I]\n\n[I][B][COLOR=#ff0000]I truly wish you could have spared me[/COLOR][/B][/I], \n \n\nLet''s sing it in [I]orchestra[/I], lolz!\n\n\nLets see what happens by the time you''re ready, your purchase is till couple of months ahead.\n\n\nRegards.', 1, 1, '119.153.53.93', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
